data.text: Incorporated in 2002 with headquarters in Al Shuwaikh, Kuwait. Al Argan National General Trading and Contracting is a limited liability company operating within the Real Estate sector. The company specializes in providing real estate construction, development and project management services for commercial and residential projects. The company has subsidiaries domiciled in Kuwait, Bahrain and Qatar. The company is a subsidiary of Al Argan International Real Estate Company KSCP in Kuwait. Al Argan National General Trading and Contracting is a private company.
